# v2 Universal App вҖ“ Build Walkthrough

## What Was Built

Three files were updated and committed to the `feature/universal-app` branch.

---

## вҡҷпёҸ 1. Universal Profile System ([app.js](file:///d:/AI%20Coding%20Projects/AntigravityTimesheetApp/app.js))

All hardcoded personal strings were replaced with a [getProfile()](file:///d:/AI%20Coding%20Projects/AntigravityTimesheetApp/app.js#17-21) function that reads from `localStorage`. This means any user can configure the app without touching code.

**Profile fields stored:**
- `userName`, `employerName`, `employerEmail`, `syncEmail`
- `hourlyRate` (default: $26/hr)
- `payPeriod`, `payDateType`, `payDateVal`
- `pdfFormat`, `syncEnabled`

---

## вҡҷпёҸ 2. Settings Modal ([index.html](file:///d:/AI%20Coding%20Projects/AntigravityTimesheetApp/index.html) + [app.js](file:///d:/AI%20Coding%20Projects/AntigravityTimesheetApp/app.js))

A full-screen settings overlay accessible via the **вҡҷпёҸ button** in the app header.

![Settings Modal](file:///C:/Users/mello/.gemini/antigravity/brain/39a8dfe2-51d3-4e0d-9cd8-4ad47880eeba/settings_modal_top_1774498474857.png)

All fields are pre-populated from the profile and saved back to `localStorage` on "Save Profile."

